    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/5fdda3c3726af0c3f94712bf317e2b31.avif?t=1770371356\" width=616 height=66 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/71b8e4ce58f744de7b63495e445e4813.avif?t=1770371356\" width=616 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kosmocean, a planet covered by water, where humans survive on tiny islands, and factions lay spread across the sea - Viridis islands, that bordered on a pastoral lands, Utopia platform with its ancient steel Submarines, Cult of Noun and its Firetop Mountain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Ikki, a young boy living on a small island with his intrepid grandfather who taught him everything he knows. Together they built Bathys, a pocket submarine, using recyled material, flotsom and jetsom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/c29f34369bbe3bb2a0896758104699fd.poster.avif?t=1770371356\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/c29f34369bbe3bb2a0896758104699fd.webm?t=1770371356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/c29f34369bbe3bb2a0896758104699fd.mp4?t=1770371356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/a86497c98247ce6ad5615da5504ec79c.poster.avif?t=1770371356\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/a86497c98247ce6ad5615da5504ec79c.webm?t=1770371356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/a86497c98247ce6ad5615da5504ec79c.mp4?t=1770371356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a catastrophe, our heros are separated. All that is left is the incomplete logbook. Ikki's quest begins : he must find his grandfather.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll descend miles below the surface, where the sun never shines, where terrible currents, monstrous creatures and terrifying pressure are an insurmountable barrier to your progress. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Where the ocean seems to have no bottom, a new world beneath the sea may hold the key to the survival of humanity… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will discover a detailed water world brought to life with hand-drawn animated graphics and immersive sound design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/2d9ce0ba151bf6f67fb1d38cf0aa8116.poster.avif?t=1770371356\" width=614 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/2d9ce0ba151bf6f67fb1d38cf0aa8116.webm?t=1770371356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144610/extras/2d9ce0ba151bf6f67fb1d38cf0aa8116.mp4?t=1770371356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
